                  <summary>Surah 68:9-24 and 68:36-45 (Kufan system)</summary>
                  <msItem>
                     <note type="general">Strokes mark the end of a verse and verses are numbered by tens by inclosing the appropriate letter numeral in a circle.  The verse divisions agree with that of the printed text, which follows the Kufic usage.</note>
